      <abstract>
        <t>&lt;p&gt;This document examines the use of Source-Specific Multicast (SSM) across inter-domain peering points for a specified set of deployment scenarios.  The objectives are to (1) describe the setup process for multicast-based delivery across administrative domains for these scenarios and (2) document supporting functionality to enable this process.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
